quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,"Nuun : Haala fii sugu ﾉ容e kalfe yawtiino ka fuﾉ遼熔rde cortewol Al-Baqarah. Allah woondirii ﾉ熔o karambol, O woondiri kadi ko yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n winndirta kon karammbi maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n."
  68,2,"Aan Nulaaﾉ熔 a wonaa kaangaaﾉ熔, sabu ko Allah neeminir-maa kon Annabaaku. Aan ko a danndiiﾉ熔 e feetere nde ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎 siforte."
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodan-maa mbarjaari ndi taﾆｴondirtaa e ko dokkal hay gooto e dow Ma sabu kon ronnditagol nulal ngal e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  68,4,"E ko pellet, hiﾉ預 e jikku mawngu ngu Alqur'aana ardi e mun. Ko a jikkinirﾉ熔 ko woni e mayre kon e mbaadi timmundi."
  68,5,"Aray nde tinaa an, ﾉ兎e fennooﾉ兎 kadi yi'a."
  68,6,"ﾃ疎lnde goonga feeﾃｱata, anndoton ko hommbo e mo'on woni haangaaﾉ熔."
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa an Nulaaﾉ熔 ﾉ砥ri anndude ooﾃｱiiﾉ熔 on e laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi ﾉ砥ri anndude feewuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n. Himo anndi ko kamﾉ兎 woni majjuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, an woni feewuﾉ熔 e laawol Makko ngol."
  68,8,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, wata a tewto fennooﾉ兎 ko adduﾉ預a kon."
  68,9,"Hiﾉ兎 yiﾉ擁 si a newantono ﾉ兎 e innde diina, kamﾉ兎 kadi ﾉ兎 newano-maa."
  68,10,"Wata a tewto kadi kala ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 woondirgol meere, hoyﾉ熔."
  68,11,"ﾆ隔uﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 ﾃｱo'ugol yimﾉ兎, ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 yaarugol waddude yimﾉ兎 fii senndira hakkunde maﾉ橡兎."
  68,12,"ﾆ隔uﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 haﾉ蓉gol moﾆｴﾆｴere, jaggitoowo jawle e teddule e pittaali yimﾉ兎, ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 bakkaatu e geddi."
  68,13,"Yoora-ﾉ兎rndeejo, ﾅ喫ﾃｱiraaﾉ熔 heﾉ妬reede nii."
  68,14,"Fii tun o wonii jom jawdi e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎, o townitanii gomﾉ擁ngol Allah e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on."
  68,15,"Si Aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n janngaama e makko, o wi'a: Ko tinndi adinooﾉ兎 nii."
  68,16,"Men waﾉ預nay mo maande nde momtotaako ka hoore kinal makko."
  68,17,"Men jarribor ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎 kokke e heege, wano Men jarribornoo jeyﾉ兎 ngesa ba, fewndo ﾉ兎n woondunoo wonnde pellet, ﾉ兎 soﾃｱiroyay mba subaka on, hiﾉ兎 hittina fii wata miskiino ﾃｱaamu e mabba."
  68,18,"ﾆ‘ ronki ittintinnde e woondoore maﾉ橡兎 nden, wi'ugol : "Si Allah jaﾉ妬i"."
  68,19,"Allah wuurti yiite e mabba, nge ﾃｱaami ba tawi ﾉ兎 e mabba hari hiﾉ兎 ﾉ預ani, ﾉ兎 waawaali duﾃｱugol yiite e mabba."
  68,20,"Mba ﾉ殿wliri wa jemma niﾉ橡登."
  68,21,"ﾆ‘ noddindiri bimmbi law."
  68,22,"ﾆ‘ wi'i : Dawee ka ngesa mon ado waasuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n arude, si tawii ko on soﾃｱooﾉ兎 mba."
  68,23,"ﾆ‘ yahiri ka ngesa maﾉ橡兎 hiﾉ兎 sowndondira hakkunde maﾉ橡兎."
  68,24,"Hiﾉ兎 wi'indira hakkunde maﾉ橡兎 : miskiino woo naatataa ka ngesa ton hannde."
  68,25,"ﾆ‘ dawidi e eﾉ橡登ore ﾉ預wugol dimﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n."
  68,26,"Nde ﾉ兎 yi'noo ngesa mban no huﾉ橡殿, ﾉ兎 wi'i: Pellet, men majjii laawol amen ngol."
  68,27,"Wurin ko men haﾉ預aﾉ兎 suﾃｱugol dimﾉ容 amen ﾉ容n, sabu ko men eﾉ橡砥noo kon ﾉ預wugol miskimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  68,28,"ﾆ「rﾉ熔 moﾆｴﾆｴude on wi'i: Mi wi'anaano on fewndo eﾉ橡砥noﾉ熔n ﾉ預wugol waasuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n : haanii ka subhinanoﾉ熔n Allah, tuubanon Mo?"
  68,29,"ﾆ‘ wi'i : Senayee woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari men tooﾃｱitorii pittaali amen eﾉ橡砥gol ﾉ預wude waasuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ容e dimﾉ容 amen."
  68,30,"ﾆ‘ ruttitii e konngol maﾉ橡兎 ngol, hiﾉ兎 felitoo."
  68,31,"ﾆ‘ ninnsi ﾉ兎 wi'i : Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko men yawtunooﾉ兎 keeri, sabu ko men ﾉ預wi kon waasuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n haqqee maﾉ橡兎."
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana men ngesa mban. Ko ka Joomi amen tun woni ko menen men rerﾉ預nta. Men jortorii Mo yaafuyee, meﾉ容n ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ra Mo moﾆｴﾆｴere."
  68,33,"Ko sugu ﾉ容e lette haﾉ容ede arsike ﾉ熔o, woni ko Men lettirta yeddayﾉ兎 Men ﾉ兎n; ko lette laakara ﾉ容n non ﾉ砥ri mawnude, sinno hiﾉ兎 anndunoo tiiﾉ蓉gol e duumagol ﾉ容 ngol."
  68,34,"Huluﾉ兎 Allah ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔ftii yamirooje Makko ﾉ容n ﾉ兎 woﾉ遼葉itii haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n, ko pellet, hino woodani ﾉ兎 ka Joomi maﾉ橡兎, Aljannaaji neema, ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 neeminotoo e mun, ko aldaa e taﾆｴondiral."
  68,35,"Kere Men waﾉ預y juulﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wano heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka njoﾉ電i, wano sirkooﾉ兎 Makka ﾉ兎n aaﾆｴori ﾉ蓉m?"
  68,36,"Ko heﾉ妬 on onon ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎, si tawii hiﾉ熔n ﾃｱaawira ndee ﾃｱaawoore ooﾃｱiinde?"
  68,37,"Kaa hiﾉ熔n mari Deftere, nde janngoton e mun wiide ﾉ熔ftiiﾉ熔 e goopﾉ熔 no fota?"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e nde Deftere, ko ko suﾉ登ytoﾉ熔n ka laakara."
  68,39,"Kaa ko aadiiji teentinaaﾉ擁 woodani on e Amen, wonnde pellet, ko ko ﾃｱaawanﾉ熔n ko'e-mon kon woodani on?"
  68,40,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, lamndii ﾉ兎 wowlu ﾉ兎 ngol konngol ﾉ兎n, ko hommbo e maﾉ橡兎 fawtanii ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉m?"
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidaaﾉ擁 woodani ﾉ兎 gaanin Allah, fotnayﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 e gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n njoﾉ電i? Awa yo ﾉ兎 addu ﾉ擁n kafidaaﾉ擁 maﾉ橡兎, si tawii ko e goonga ﾉ兎 woni nodditorde fotnugol ﾉ兎 e gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka njoﾉ電i."
  68,42,"ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, kulol ngol feeﾃｱay, Joomi men feﾃｱﾃｱina korlal Makko ngal, yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n noddee e sujjugol : gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n sujja, heddoo heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e naafiqiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n tawde ﾉ兎 waawoytaa sujjude."
  68,43,"Hara gite maﾉ橡兎 no heli, nimse e koyeera kadi no suddi ﾉ兎. Ko tawde ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬rteno sujjangol Allah ka aduna, fewndo ka ﾉ兎 waawunoo ﾉ砥ri hanndeere nden."
  68,44,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, accidam e kala fennuﾉ熔 ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Maaﾉ預; aray nde Men soggira ﾉ兎 e lette ﾉ容n sagara-sagara ka ﾉ兎 anndataa wonnde ko fewjoori e hoore maﾉ橡兎 non."
  68,45,"Mi nennan ﾉ兎 tun e bakkatuuji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n seeﾉ預. Ko pellet, pewje Am ﾉ容n e hoore heeferﾉ兎 e fennooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ko tiiﾉ蓉ﾉ容. ﾆ‘ fuutotaako Lam, ﾉ兎 daﾉ熔ytaa kadi lette Am ﾉ容n."
  68,46,"Kaa hara an Nulaaﾉ熔 on a ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬r ﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i e ko noddataa ﾉ兎 e mun kon, hara ko yoﾉ砥gol ﾉ蓉m woni ko sattani ﾉ兎 haa tawata ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉urnoto ma? Tigi on, wanaa ﾉ蓉m. A ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬raani ﾉ兎e njoﾉ電i fes. Ko haﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 non jokkugol ma?"
  68,47,"Kaa ﾉ兎 anndu fii wirniiﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, hara ko ﾉ擁n woni ko ﾉ兎 winndirta ko waalantooﾉ兎 e hujjaaji ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 wennjire?"
  68,48,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, muﾃｱﾃｱor ko Joomi maa ﾃｱaawiri kon suynirgol ﾉ兎 nennaneede, hara a wa'aali wa Annabi Yuunusa wonndiiﾉ熔 linngii ngii, taﾆｴinooﾉ熔 e yimﾉ兎 mun tuma o noddunoo Joomi makko ka niwre maayo e niwre linngii."
  68,49,"Si wanaa fii yurmeende Joomi makko nden hewtitike mo, ko pellet, linngii ngii bugotono mbo e wulaa hara ko o felniiﾉ熔."
  68,50,"Joomi makko suﾉ妬i mo, O waﾉ擁 mo jeyaaﾉ熔 e moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  68,51,"Hay yedduﾉ兎 Allah ﾉ兎n yeddi Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on, ﾉ兎 eﾉ橡妬ino yuwirgol ma gite maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, hakkee ko ﾉ兎 puttinatno maa gite, tuma ﾉ兎 nanata ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e maaﾉ預, hara hiﾉ兎 wi'ira mbeleeﾉ容 e ﾉ蓉urnagl goonga : Oo Nulaaﾉ熔 arduﾉ熔 e ndee Deftere, ko haangaaﾉ熔."
  68,52,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e maaﾉ預 wonaali, si wanaa waaju e janntoore yimﾉ兎 e jinna."
